OL,3,CJersey Civil Service making 'good
OL,4,Cprogress' on combatting bullying
OL,6,FA 2021 report noted significant
OL,7,Fimprovements but still found examples
OL,8,Fof public arguments, aggressive
OL,9,Fbehaviour, and belittling of staff by
OL,10,Fsenior managers.
OL,12,FThe 2025 report states: "We conclude
OL,13,Fthat (the States) have continued to
OL,14,Fmake good progress.
OL,16,F"In all respects - policy, managerial
OL,17,Fawareness, quality of investigations,
OL,18,Fnumbers of complaints - (the States)
OL,19,Fhave improved the position from that
OL,20,Ffirst noted in 2018 and reviewed in
OL,21,F2021."
