OL,4,Cprogress' on combatting bullying
OL,6,FWhile the new report highlights
OL,7,Ffurther areas for progress, it adds
OL,8,Fthat aspects of the Civil Service's
OL,9,Fwork to improve its services were
OL,10,Fbetter than "what other like-minded
OL,11,Femployers offer".
OL,13,FIn his first interview since taking on
OL,14,Fthe Civil Service Chief Executive
OL,15,Frole, Dr Andrew McLaughlin says the
OL,16,Fbullying was "certainly something I
OL,17,Fwas aware of" but that the situation
OL,18,Fhas improved.
