OL,3,CJersey Civil Service making 'good
OL,4,Cprogress' on combatting bullying
OL,6,FHe explains: "We've just had a piece
OL,7,Fdone which shows that aspect of public
OL,8,Fservices is improving significantly.
OL,10,F"It's not been a big feature of my
OL,11,Ftime in the public service.
OL,13,F"What I observe most every day is just
OL,14,Fpublic servants getting on with their
OL,15,Fjob, trying to improve the life of
OL,16,Fislanders.
