OL,3,CJersey Civil Service making 'good
OL,4,Cprogress' on combatting bullying
OL,6,F"The public service has got a very
OL,7,Fclear set of values and a zero
OL,8,Ftolerance of poor behaviour in
OL,9,Fgeneral, particularly when it comes to
OL,10,Fpoor behaviour in the form of
OL,11,Fbullying, and it just won't be
OL,12,Ftolerated.
OL,14,F"I think we've shown an improving
OL,15,Ftrend over the past couple of years."
OL,17,FDr McLaughlin became the interim head
OL,18,Fof the Civil Service in September 2023
OL,19,Ffollowing the resignation of Suzanne
OL,20,FWiley.
