OL,6,FHe was then given a new contract from
OL,7,F1 July 2024 with a six-month review
OL,8,Fperiod to continue in the position.
OL,10,FDr McLaughlin adds: "I've just been
OL,11,Fblessed to have had such a varied
OL,12,Fcareer.
OL,14,F"All I do, and I think every leader is
OL,15,Fthe same, is trying to ensure that
OL,16,Fwhen I leave the place, it's in better
OL,17,Fshape than when I found it."
